, turmeric and reserved ground spices then sauté <b>4 min\/100°C\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add tomatoes, fresh coriander, water, stock cube, salt and half the reserved chopped spinach then blend <b>1 min\/speed 8<b>."},{"content":"Add chicken and remaining reserved chopped spinach then cook <b>12 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add 100 g yoghurt and lemon juice then stir in with spatula. Serve warm, drizzled with remaining 50 g yoghurt, with rice or Indian bread."}],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","50m","6 portions"]}